1. Get ProofGeneral and get it working in Emacs. The source code and installation
guide are at 'http://proofgeneral.inf.ed.ac.uk/download'.
2. Untar abella.tar.gz in the top of the ProofGeneral directory.
3. place proof-site.el in ProofGeneral/generic/.
4. Add these two lines to your .emacs:

  (load-file "/wherever/ProofGeneral/generic/proof-site.el")
  (load-file "/wherever/abella/emacs/lprolog.el")